Bound every started Content-Length frame read.

A completely idle MCP pipe remains open.  Once its first byte arrives, start
one absolute deadline that covers the first line, all remaining headers, and
the body.  Reject inherited overrides longer than the declared 10-second
phase, and never resynchronize after a partial request.

--- a/anvil-stdio.sh
+++ b/anvil-stdio.sh
@@ -312,7 +312,7 @@
